---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import web3Desktop from "@/assets/image-web-3-desktop.jpg";
import web3Mobile from "@/assets/image-web-3-mobile.jpg";
---

<article>
  <div>
    <Image src={web3Desktop} alt="Web 3.0" class="hidden sm:block" loading="eager" format="webp" />
    <Image src={web3Mobile} alt="Web 3.0" class="block sm:hidden" loading="eager" format="webp" />
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-x-8 gap-y-4 lg:flex-row">
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
        <h1 class="text-theme-very-dark-blue text-[2.5rem] leading-[1] font-extrabold lg:text-6xl">
          The Bright Future of Web 3.0?
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col justify-between gap-y-4">
        <p class="text-theme-dark-grayish-blue leading-6">
          We dive into the next evolution of the web that claims to put the power of the platforms
          back into the hands of the people. But is it really fulfilling its promise?
        </p>
        <a
          href="/"
          class="bg-theme-soft-red text-theme-very-dark-blue hover:bg-theme-very-dark-blue hover:text-theme-off-white w-1/2 px-6 py-3 text-center font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase transition-colors delay-100 sm:w-1/3 lg:w-1/2"
          >Read more</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>
